0Z","msg":"don't interview chi na shit anymore...they don't pay attention to anything. they know nothing apart from how much they have in their pockets"},{"pid":"246d074a0719b85beaac4a8c5bf9d18561e8454d","tid":1588684,"uid":183536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:34:18.000Z","msg":"#國際戰線<br />\n#黃<br />\n#形象工程<br />\n#和理非必做<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以只係顧自己， 我哋要將黃藍經濟圈推出國際🌏!<br />\n<br />\n#黃金經濟圈 #香港抗爭者 #撐澳洲 之 #贊助樹熊挑戰 <br />\n<br />\n近期澳洲🇦🇺有大規模山火🔥，只要捐款小小錢救1隻🐨(AUD40=HKD213)，就可以幫香港抗爭者加少少光環🌟!<br />\n<br />\n唔使等前線，和理非快黎救🐨! 做好啲個形像，第日移民🐌或者去旅行💼，好多🦘都會感激我哋㗎!<br />\n<br />\n1. 上樹熊醫院🏥網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.koalahospital.org.au/adopt-a-koala\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.koalahospital.org.au%2Fadopt-a-koala&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=3289eac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.koalahospital.org.au/adopt-a-koala</a><br />\n2. 揀隻可愛樹熊🐨<br />\n3. 揀✔ EAdoption<br />\n4. 地區係香港，地址隨意📝<br />\n3. 填你個名(可考慮:爭取普選)➡️Hong Kong Universal Suffragists<br />\n4. 去check out購物車🛒<br />\n5. 填信用卡💳號碼等資料<br />\n6. 完成<br />\n7. 🐨certificate 寄到你電郵📧<br />\n8. 可以reply及貼到我的tweeter，已tag了澳洲傳媒及政客!推到上報📰!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LoveProtestinHK/status/1214604066602377216?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLoveProtestinHK%2Fstatus%2F1214604066602377216%3Fs%3D09&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=a9f8ad99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLoveProtestinHK%2Fstatus%2F1214604066602377216%3Fs%3D09&h=5eacc668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LoveProtestinHK/status/1214604066602377216?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n大家快點行動，🐨🐨好需要我們。澳洲都推動緊Magnitsky Act，通過左先可以制裁⚔⚔到中共走狗🐕教育局長楊潤雄🐊!"}]}